ungen auftragen</entry></row><row><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" rowsep="1" valign="top">g)</entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" rowsep="1" valign="top">plastische Veränderungen an Darstellern herstellen und einschminken</entry></row><row><entry VJ="1" align="right" colsep="0" morerows="4" rowsep="1" valign="top">15</entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" morerows="4" rowsep="1" valign="top">Gestalten von Frisuren mit Eigenhaar und Haarteilen (§ 3 Nr. 15)</entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" valign="top">a)</entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" valign="top">Haarlängen bestimmen</entry><entry VJ="1" align="center" colsep="0" morerows="2" rowsep="1" valign="middle">10</entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" morerows="2" rowsep="1" valign="top"> </entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" morerows="2" rowsep="1" valign="top"> </entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" morerows="2" rowsep="1" valign="top"> </entry></row><row><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" valign="top">b)</entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" valign="top">Schneidtechniken auswählen und anwenden</entry></row><row><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" rowsep="1" valign="top">c)</entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" rowsep="1" valign="top">Frisuren, insbesondere durch Wickeln, Wellen, Papillotiertechniken und Ondulation, gestalten</entry></row><row><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" valign="top">d)</entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" valign="top">Schling- und Stecktechniken anwenden</entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" morerows="1" rowsep="1" valign="top"> </entry><entry VJ="1" align="center" colsep="0" morerows="1" rowsep="1" valign="middle">12</entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" morerows="1" rowsep="1" valign="top"> </entry><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" morerows="1" rowsep="1" valign="top"> </entry></row><row><entry VJ="1" align="left" colsep="0" rowsep="1" valign="top">e)</entry><entry VJ="1" align="lef